e=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 07, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nfr1690356961256.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nfr1690356961256.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nfr1690356961256.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eqm1665702780519\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"eqm1665702780519__copy_and_paste_objects_and_text_17243\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To copy and paste objects, properties and text in the Uniface IDE, right-click and\n                choose the appropriate command from the context menu.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eqm1665702780519__li_d1571e1_d1572e1_d1573e1\">To copy an object or text, right-click the object and\n                                then choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Copy</span> in the context menu.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eqm1665702780519__li_d1574e1_d1575e1_d1576e1\">To paste an object or text, right-click an object or an\n                                area where the object should be pasted and then click\n                                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste</span>, or choose another\n                                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste</span> option (such as\n                                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste as Child</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste\n                                        Before</span>, or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste After</span>).\n                                If the copied object is not valid in the target context, it cannot\n                                be pasted (and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste</span> option(s) are not\n                                available in the context menu).</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eqm1665702780519__li_d1577e1_d1578e1_d1579e1\">When you copy a Uniface object such as a modeled field,\n                                and paste it into a code editor or another text editor, the\n                                fully-qualified name of the object is copied.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eqm1665702780519__li_d1580e1_d1581e1_d1582e1\">When you copy a Snippet from the Resource Browser into\n                                the Script Editor or Layout Editor, the content of the Snippet is\n                                pasted.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eqm1665702780519__li_d1583e1_d1584e1_d1585e1\">In the Script Editor and Layout Editor, you can use\n                                conventional keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+C and Ctrl+V). This is not\n                                possible in other locations.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">You can also insert or copy/paste fields in the Structure pane, but not in the Canvas\n                                pane. You can insert or copy/paste multiple fields in one attempt in\n                                the Structure pane.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4443671\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4443671\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Copy and Paste Objects and Text Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 07, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 To copy and paste objects, properties and text in the Uniface IDE, right-click and choose the appropriate command from the context menu. To copy an object or text, right-click the object and then choose Copy in the context menu. To paste an object or text, right-click an object or an area where the object should be pasted and then click Paste , or choose another Paste option (such as Paste as Child , Paste Before , or Paste After ). If the copied object is not valid in the target context, it cannot be pasted (and the Paste option(s) are not available in the context menu). When you copy a Uniface object such as a modeled field, and paste it into a code editor or another text editor, the fully-qualified name of the object is copied. When you copy a Snippet from the Resource Browser into the Script Editor or Layout Editor, the content of the Snippet is pasted. In the Script Editor and Layout Editor, you can use conventional keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+C and Ctrl+V). This is not possible in other locations. You can also insert or copy/paste fields in the Structure pane, but not in the Canvas pane. You can insert or copy/paste multiple fields in one attempt in the Structure pane. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}